 relevancy. Technologies under consideration include but not limited to autonomy enablers, power generation (Tactical Range Extender Enhanced (TREE), electric
 Power Export and Expansion Kit (ePEEK),signature management, winter tires, Counter Unmanned Aircraft Systems (cUAS) capabilities, and improved force protection.




