as well as 360 degree coverage (rotating). The AN/TPQ-53 system incorporates Multi-Mission Radar (MMR) software into the system baseline, enabling air surveillance
for Commander's situational awareness of Unmanned Aerial Systems (UAS). The AN/TPQ-53 system interoperates with mission command systems to provide the
