 FY 2027 RDTE funds support software regression testing and full material release for Distributed Digital Receiver Exciter (DDREX) Capability Sets #1 and #2 to
 enhance system survivability, electronic protection (EP), and bandwidth agility to improve system capability in a threat environment. FY 2027 funds also continue
