A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
Self-Propelled Howitzer Modernization effort improves self-propelled howitzer lethality through increased range and increased rate of fire, using mature technology to
improve mobility, survivability, reliability, supportability, and lethality. This effort will analyze and evaluate new cannon technology, including existing and future artillery
systems as well as technology to improve mission cycle time and enable future platform autonomy. This effort will also inform requirements, release request for vendor
proposals and evaluate vendor offerings.

