D. Acquisition Strategy
The Avenger MOD-SLEP addresses obsolescence of key components and ensures that Avenger is viable and sustainable through the end of its economic useful life.

 The MOD-SLEP components are the TC, the AFCC, the Mode 5 IFF, the VIC-5, the M3P machine gun and A-PNT. The M3P machine gun will be fielded through
 attrition. The other MOD-SLEP components will be installed in the field.

 Development and testing of hardware and software modifications necessary to fully integrate the A-PNT capability into the Avenger will be performed by a combination
 of Government and Original Equipment Manufacturer efforts, using the existing and new Engineering Service contracts. A-PNT modifications will be performed by Depot
 Maintenance teams.




